{"segment":37,"line_start":947,"line_end":967,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"啊哟，不好！蜈蚣的剧毒都给我搬入肚里了！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":949,"line_end":951},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"这本书上本来明明有字没图，怎地忽然文字不见了，却多了个古怪的和尚？我无意之间，居然做出跟这和尚一般的姿势？这和尚定是菩萨，来救我性命的。","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":951,"line_end":955}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":38,"line_start":969,"line_end":989,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"啊","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":973,"line_end":973},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"你干什么？怎么你还没死？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":973,"line_end":973},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"小人⋯⋯小人还没死！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":973,"line_end":973},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"原来她只道我已早死了。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":973,"line_end":973},{"speaker":"char_you_tan_zhi","speaker_name":"游坦之","listener":null,"text":"你没死那也好！快穿好衣服，跟我再出去捉毒虫。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":974,"line_end":976},{"speaker":"char_you_tan_zhi","speaker_name":"游坦之","listener":null,"text":"是！","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":976,"line_end":976}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":39,"line_start":991,"line_end":1011,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ah_zi","speaker_name":"阿紫","listener":null,"text":"伏低！","tone":"激动","chapter":28,"line_start":993,"line_end":993},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"怎么办？要是蟒蛇将木鼎撞坏了，岂不糟糕？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":28,"line_start":1001,"line_end":1003},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"不要紧，我去将蛇赶开！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":1003,"line_end":1005}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":40,"line_start":1013,"line_end":1035,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"这条蚕儿好厉害，看来是毒物中的大王了。","tone":"焦急","chapter":28,"line_start":1023,"line_end":1025},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"如此剧毒的蚕虫倘若来吸我的血，这一次可性命难保了。","tone":"焦急","chapter":28,"line_start":1025,"line_end":1027},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"快追，快追！","tone":"焦急","chapter":28,"line_start":1033,"line_end":1033}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":41,"line_start":1037,"line_end":1061,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"你也不追得快些，这时候却又到那里找去？我不管，你非给我捉回来不可！","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":1041,"line_end":1043},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"说什么也得给我捉了来，否则不用再来见我。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":28,"line_start":1045,"line_end":1047},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"姑娘，姑娘，我找到了！","tone":"激动","chapter":28,"line_start":1051,"line_end":1053},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"悯忠寺","tone":"焦急","chapter":28,"line_start":1057,"line_end":1057}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":42,"line_start":1063,"line_end":1085,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"你怎地如此不守规矩，独个儿偷偷出去玩耍？害得老子耽心了半天，生怕你从此不回来了。老子从昆仑山巅万里迢迢的将你带来，你太也不知好歹，不懂老子对待你一片苦心。这样下去，你还有什么出息？将来自毁前途，谁也不会来可怜你！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":28,"line_start":1065,"line_end":1071},{"speaker":"char_you_tan_zhi","speaker_name":"游坦之","listener":null,"text":"他说什么从昆仑山巅万里迢迢的将他带来，多半是师父或是长辈，不是父亲。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1073,"line_end":1075},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"这圆圈是用药物画的，这药物是那蚕儿的克星。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1083,"line_end":1085}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":43,"line_start":1087,"line_end":1117,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"原来是个酒肉和尚。看来这条蚕儿是他所养，而且他极之宝爱。却怎么去盗了来？","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1089,"line_end":1093},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"慧净，慧净！","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1095,"line_end":1097},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"慧净，慧净，你不去做晚课，躲到那里去啦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":1099,"line_end":1101},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"我在锄菜哪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1101,"line_end":1103},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"晨课晚课，人人要做！什么时候不好锄菜，却在晚课时分来锄？快去，快去！做完晚课，再来锄菜好了。在悯忠寺挂单，就得守悯忠寺的规矩。难道你少林寺就没庙规家法吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":1103,"line_end":1109},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"是！","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":1109,"line_end":1111},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"这大肚和尚原来是少林寺的。少林和尚个个身有武功，我偷他蚕儿，可得加倍小心。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1113,"line_end":1115},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"未知","listener":null,"text":"却如何捉它？","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":1115,"line_end":1117}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
